Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近年来要死也这么麻烦啊！
